item.title: AutoKeras - A Quick Introduction and Demostration
item.description: Getting started with AutoKeras AutoKeras is an open-source AutoML library built on top of TensorFlow, designed to simplify the process of building and training deep learning models without requiring extensive knowledge of model architecture and hyperparameter tuning.
